Module kivakit.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.values.count

Class MutableCount

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.values.count.MutableCount
All Implemented Interfaces:
Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject, Countable, Listener, Transceiver, Comparable<MutableCount>
public class MutableCount extends Object implements Countable, Comparable<MutableCount>, Listener
A mutable count value useful in lambdas and inner classes. Can be increment()ed, decrement()ed, added to with plus(long) and plus(long) and converted to different types with asCount() and asLong().
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
